com.facebook.buck.rules

Class Cell

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.facebook.buck.rules.Cell

  • public class Cell
extends Object
    Represents a single checkout of a code base. Two cells model the same code base if their underlying ProjectFilesystems are equal.
